1972;;The Wrath of God;;American;;Ralph Nelson;;Robert Mitchum, Frank Langella, Rita Hayworth;;western;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Wrath_of_God;;Van Horne (played by Mitchum), a bank robber dressed like a Roman Catholic priest, is spared from a firing squad in 1922 in an unnamed Central America nation and sent to kill a local desperado.